Primary Benefit: Supports hormonal balance, menstrual regularity, and PMS relief.
description: A powder made from the fruit of the chaste tree. It is widely used to support female hormonal balance, help regulate the menstrual cycle, and alleviate symptoms of premenstrual syndrome (PMS).

Primary Benefit: Extremely high in antioxidants; supports cellular health.
description: A superfood powder made from freeze-dried acai berries from the Amazon. It is incredibly rich in antioxidants, which help combat free radical damage, and is also a source of healthy fats and fiber.
